---
---

<section class="section" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem__layout">

      <div class="problem__left reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">The problem</p>
        <h2 id="problem-heading">
          Most B2B companies are invisible on LinkedIn.
        </h2>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem__right">
        <div class="vis-placeholder problem__visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>Visual placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <p class="problem__lead reveal reveal-delay-1">
          They post sporadically. Their company page is outdated. Their executives have no presence.
          Their ads reach the wrong people.
        </p>
        <p class="problem__close reveal reveal-delay-2">
          LinkedIn rewards consistency and expertise. Without both, you're wasting the best
          B2B channel available.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .problem__visual {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    min-height: 240px;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-8);
  }

  .problem__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .problem__close {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .vis-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,102,194,0.06) 0%, rgba(0,168,220,0.09) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    border: 1.5px dashed rgba(10,102,194,0.22);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(10,102,194,0.35);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.10em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .problem__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-10); }
  }
</style>
